HEADWORD: Trampler
<hw>Tram"pler</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>One who tramples;
one who treads down; <as>as, a <ex>trampler</ex> on nature's
law</as>.</def> <rj><au>Cowper.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
